<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ men yī tóng zhàn zài nǐ de miàn qián. zhān yǎng nǐ de róng měi róng yán.
 wǒ men hǎo xiàng nǐ diàn zhōng de qīng gǎn lǎn shù,\001qīng qīng de gǎn lǎn.
 cóng shēn yè dào tiān liàng, yuàn yì hé nǐ jiāo tán yī shēng yuàn yì zhù zài nǐ de diàn;
 yuàn yì gěi nǐ kàn mén kàn shǒu pú táo yuán, nǐ zhè lǐ yǒu shēng mìng píng ān.</lyrics>
<title>yǒng zhù shén de diàn 迦南286</title>
<hymn_number>286</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>